title: Did Sarah Palin Say ‘US Already Attacked Iran Back When It Called Itself Iraq’?
subtitle: "It’s like when Puff Daddy changed his name to P Diddy," Palin also reportedly said. "You’re not fooling anyone, Iraq."
author: David Mikkelson
vclaim: Sarah Palin asserted in June 2019 that the U.S. had "already attacked Iran back when it called itself Iraq."
